---
layout: base.njk
title: "Service Areas - Cutting Edge Concrete Cutting"
description: "Find concrete cutting services in your area. We serve Los Angeles, Orange, Ventura, Riverside, San Bernardino, Kern, Tulare, Fresno, Kings, and Madera Counties."
---

<main class="service-areas-page">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Service Areas</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Professional concrete cutting, sawing, and coring services throughout Southern and Central California</p>
    
    <div class="counties-grid">
      {% for area in serviceAreas %}
      <div class="county-card">
        <h2>{{ area.county }}</h2>
        <p class="county-description">{{ area.meta.description }}</p>
        
        <div class="cities-section">
          <h3>Cities We Serve:</h3>
          <ul class="cities-list">
            {% for city in area.serviceArea %}
            <li><a href="/service-areas/{{ area.slug }}/{{ city.slug }}/">{{ city.name }}</a></li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/service-areas/{{ area.slug }}/" class="btn btn-primary">View {{ area.county }} Services</a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    
    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>Don't See Your City?</h2>
      <p>We serve many more areas throughout California. Contact us to see if we can help with your concrete cutting project.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
